REFERENCE LIBRARIES (not vendored)

team-forge can consult external curated agent/skill corpora as prior art during
Phase-3 asset discovery. Their files are NOT included in this repository — only a
pinned-commit manifest (reference-libraries/<name>.yaml) is. When a forge run
needs one, the pinned commit is fetched on demand into a local cache and adapted
(reference-and-adapt), never copied wholesale.

* ECC — https://github.com/affaan-m/ECC — MIT License, Copyright (c) 2026 Affaan Mustafa.
  Pinned in reference-libraries/ecc.yaml. If you materialize it (via
  tools/fetch_reference.py), ECC's MIT terms govern that copy.
